</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C. Rejoice, O Mother Church,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">           Am                 C          Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   all resplendant with the glory of her Lord.
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                      G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   Let this place resound,
