</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   and with His blood that he shed out of love,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">             G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   He wiped away the condemnation
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                   Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   of the ancient fault.
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">           F       E
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   This is the Passover
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">       F                           E
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   in which the true Lamb is sacrificed;
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">        F        E
