</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   this is the night
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">        F                                       E
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">   in which you have conquered the darkness of sin;

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">               Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">A. THIS IS THE NIGHT
